  <entry>
    <title>hexo 7.7 版本 自定义样式文件失效</title>
    <url>/2020/01/07/hexo%207.7%20%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%20%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>**</p>
<h2 id="由于版本升级失效的文件，可以通过自定义加引用的方式："><a href="#由于版本升级失效的文件，可以通过自定义加引用的方式：" class="headerlink" title="由于版本升级失效的文件，可以通过自定义加引用的方式："></a>由于版本升级失效的文件，可以通过自定义加引用的方式：</h2><p>**</p>
<p>没有custom.styl文件<br>可以自行创建<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200107104801342.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<p>然后在~\themes\next-reloaded\source\css的main.styl文件末尾加入引用<br>//My Layer<br>//————————————————–<br>@import “_custom/custom.styl”;</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>HEXO 搭建博客问题</category>
      </categories>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>Python修改文件中的内容</title>
    <url>/2020/01/03/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8BPython%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> os</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">alter</span><span class="params">(file,old_str,new_str)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#   :param file: 文件路径</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#   :param old_str: 需要替换的字符串</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#   :param new_str: 替换的字符串</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">with</span> open(file, <span class="string">"r"</span>, encoding=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f1,open(<span class="string">"%s.bak"</span> % file, <span class="string">"w"</span>, encoding=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f2:</span><br><span class="line">        le=<span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> lin <span class="keyword">in</span> f1:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> le&gt;=<span class="number">5</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                s = lin.split(<span class="string">" "</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                lin = s[<span class="number">0</span>] + <span class="string">" "</span>+s[<span class="number">2</span>]+<span class="string">"\n"</span>            </span><br><span class="line">            le+=<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            f2.write(lin)</span><br><span class="line">    os.remove(file)</span><br><span class="line">    os.rename(<span class="string">f"file.bak"</span>, file)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">alter(<span class="string">r"1.txt"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Python</category>
      </categories>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>JAVAEE 关于spring整合struts2和hibernate(超详细，附带配置文件示例以及整合struts出现的奇葩错误)</title>
    <url>/2019/12/30/JAVAEE%20%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Espring%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88struts2%E5%92%8Chibernate(%E8%B6%85%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%84%E5%B8%A6%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88struts%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%87%E8%91%A9%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF)/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、整合struts2"><a href="#一、整合struts2" class="headerlink" title="一、整合struts2"></a>一、整合struts2</h2><p><strong>要特别注意struts2、hibernate、spring的版本下述方法对于struts2.1、hibernate3.3.2、spring3.0.5有效</strong>(版本不匹配会导致很多问题，卡了俺超长时间)</p>
<p><strong>遇到下述问题：</strong><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20191230145716685.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3FxXzQyMTg4MTY4,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br><strong>将applicationContext.xml文件复制到src目录下一份即可解决。</strong></p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p>/WEB-INF/web.xml配置</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">"1.0"</span> encoding=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;web-app xmlns:xsi=<span class="string">"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"</span> xmlns=<span class="string">"http://xmlns.jcp.org/xml/ns/javaee"</span> xsi:schemaLocation=<span class="string">"http://xmlns.jcp.org/xml/ns/javaee http://xmlns.jcp.org/xml/ns/javaee/web-app_3_1.xsd"</span> version=<span class="string">"3.1"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;display-name&gt;plane2&lt;/display-name&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;listener&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;listener-<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span>&gt;<span class="title">org</span>.<span class="title">springframework</span>.<span class="title">web</span>.<span class="title">context</span>.<span class="title">ContextLoaderListener</span>&lt;/<span class="title">listener</span>-<span class="title">class</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">  &lt;/<span class="title">listener</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">  //&lt;<span class="title">context</span>-<span class="title">param</span>&gt;  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">    //&lt;<span class="title">param</span>-<span class="title">name</span>&gt;<span class="title">contextConfigLocation</span>&lt;/<span class="title">param</span>-<span class="title">name</span>&gt;  </span></span><br><span class="line">  //  &lt;param-value&gt;classpath*:config/applicationContext.xml&lt;/param-value&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//&lt;/context-param&gt;	(默认去/WEB-INF/applicationContext.xml 下找)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  &lt;filter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;filter-name&gt;struts2&lt;/filter-name&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;filter-<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span>&gt;<span class="title">org</span>.<span class="title">apache</span>.<span class="title">struts2</span>.<span class="title">dispatcher</span>.<span class="title">ng</span>.<span class="title">filter</span>.<span class="title">StrutsPrepareAndExecuteFilter</span>&lt;/<span class="title">filter</span>-<span class="title">class</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">  &lt;/<span class="title">filter</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">  &lt;<span class="title">filter</span>-<span class="title">mapping</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">    &lt;<span class="title">filter</span>-<span class="title">name</span>&gt;<span class="title">struts2</span>&lt;/<span class="title">filter</span>-<span class="title">name</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">    &lt;<span class="title">url</span>-<span class="title">pattern</span>&gt;/*&lt;/<span class="title">url</span>-<span class="title">pattern</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">  &lt;/<span class="title">filter</span>-<span class="title">mapping</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&lt;/<span class="title">web</span>-<span class="title">app</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>/src/struts.xml</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">"1.0"</span> encoding=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span> ?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE struts PUBLIC <span class="string">"-//Apache Software Foundation//DTD Struts Configuration 2.1//EN"</span> <span class="string">"http://struts.apache.org/dtds/struts-2.1.dtd"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;struts&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     &lt;<span class="keyword">package</span> name=<span class="string">"form"</span> extends=<span class="string">"struts-default"</span> namespace=<span class="string">"/"</span> &gt;</span><br><span class="line">     </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"RegisterAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"RegisterAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"register"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/login.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"LoginAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"LoginAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"login"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/userMain.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="no"&gt;/login.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="adminmain"&gt;/adminmain.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"changepassAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.changepassAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"change"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/changepasssuccess.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="no"&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"modifyuserAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.modifyuserAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"modi"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/info.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="no"&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"realmodifyuserAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.realmodifyuserAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"modify"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/userMain.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="no"&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"havingflightAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.havingflightAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"have"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="showingflight"&gt;/showflight.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">				&lt;result name="playflight"&gt;/playflight.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="no"&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"myzhifubaoAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.myzhifubaoAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"zhifu"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/zhifusuccess.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="error"&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"firmAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.firmAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"afirm"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/afirm.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="dinerror"&gt;/dinerror.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"showorderAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.showorderAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"show"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="showingorder"&gt;/showorder.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="error"&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">				&lt;result name="back"&gt;/back.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">			&lt;action name=<span class="string">"backticketAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.backticketAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"back"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/backsuccess.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="error"&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;action name=<span class="string">"insertflightAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.insertflightAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"insert"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/adminmain.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="error"&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">	 </span><br><span class="line">			&lt;action name=<span class="string">"makeflightAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.makeflightAction"</span> method=<span class="string">"make"</span>&gt; </span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="success"&gt;/makeingflight.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">			&lt;result name="error"&gt;/error.jsp&lt;/result&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/action&gt; </span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/package&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	&lt;constant name="struts.objectFactory" value="spring"&gt;&lt;/constant&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;/struts&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>applicationContext.xml (配置 在src下)</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">"1.0"</span> encoding=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;beans</span><br><span class="line">	xmlns=<span class="string">"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans"</span></span><br><span class="line">    xmlns:xsi=<span class="string">"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    xmlns:context=<span class="string">"http://www.springframework.org/schema/context"</span></span><br><span class="line">    xmlns:tx=<span class="string">"http://www.springframework.org/schema/tx"</span></span><br><span class="line">    xsi:schemaLocation=<span class="string">"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans/spring-beans.xsd</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop/spring-aop-3.0.xsd</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">         http://www.springframework.org/schema/context http://www.springframework.org/schema/context/spring-context-3.0.xsd</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        http://www.springframework.org/schema/tx http://www.springframework.org/schema/tx/spring-tx-3.0.xsd"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"loginAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.loginAction"</span>&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"RegisterAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.RegisterAction"</span>&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">		&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"passenger"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.po.passenger"</span>&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"passengerDAO"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.dao.passengerDAO"</span> &gt;</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		 </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"passengerService"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.service.passengerService"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name=<span class="string">"pa"</span> ref=<span class="string">"passengerDAO"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"transactionManager"</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.HibernateTransactionManager"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;property name=<span class="string">"sessionFactory"</span> ref=<span class="string">"sessionFactory"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;tx:annotation-driven transaction-manager=<span class="string">"transactionManager"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"sessionFactory"</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.LocalSessionFactoryBean"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;property name=<span class="string">"configLocation"</span></span><br><span class="line">			value=<span class="string">"classpath:hibernate.cfg.xml"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/beans&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="二、整合hibernate"><a href="#二、整合hibernate" class="headerlink" title="二、整合hibernate"></a>二、整合hibernate</h2><p>/WEB-INF/applicationContext.xml</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">"1.0"</span> encoding=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;beans</span><br><span class="line">	xmlns=<span class="string">"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans"</span></span><br><span class="line">    xmlns:xsi=<span class="string">"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    xmlns:context=<span class="string">"http://www.springframework.org/schema/context"</span></span><br><span class="line">    xmlns:tx=<span class="string">"http://www.springframework.org/schema/tx"</span></span><br><span class="line">    xsi:schemaLocation=<span class="string">"http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans/spring-beans.xsd</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop http://www.springframework.org/schema/aop/spring-aop-3.0.xsd</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">         http://www.springframework.org/schema/context http://www.springframework.org/schema/context/spring-context-3.0.xsd</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        http://www.springframework.org/schema/tx http://www.springframework.org/schema/tx/spring-tx-3.0.xsd"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"loginAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.loginAction"</span>&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"RegisterAction"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.action.RegisterAction"</span>&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">		&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"passenger"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.po.passenger"</span>&gt;	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"passengerDAO"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.dao.passengerDAO"</span> &gt;</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		 </span><br><span class="line">		&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"passengerService"</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"com.service.passengerService"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name=<span class="string">"pa"</span> ref=<span class="string">"passengerDAO"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"transactionManager"</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.HibernateTransactionManager"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;property name=<span class="string">"sessionFactory"</span> ref=<span class="string">"sessionFactory"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;tx:annotation-driven transaction-manager=<span class="string">"transactionManager"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;bean id=<span class="string">"sessionFactory"</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.LocalSessionFactoryBean"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;property name=<span class="string">"configLocation"</span></span><br><span class="line">			value=<span class="string">"classpath:hibernate.cfg.xml"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;/beans&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>/src/hibernate.cfg.xml</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">"1.0"</span> encoding=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE hibernate-configuration PUBLIC</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="string">"-//Hibernate/Hibernate Configuration DTD 3.0//EN"</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="string">"http://hibernate.sourceforge.net/hibernate-configuration-3.0.dtd"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">&lt;hibernate-configuration&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;session-factory&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 配置关于数据库连接的四个项 driverClass url username password --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 设置连接提供者 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- &lt;property name=<span class="string">"hibernate.connection.provider_class"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">		org.hibernate.connection.C3P0ConnectionProvider</span><br><span class="line">		&lt;/property&gt; --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- c3p0连接池的配置 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- &lt;property name="hibernate.c3p0.max_size"&gt;20&lt;/property&gt; --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 最大连接池 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- &lt;property name="hibernate.c3p0.min_size"&gt;5&lt;/property&gt; --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 最小连接数 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- &lt;property name="hibernate.c3p0.timeout"&gt;120&lt;/property&gt; --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 超时 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- &lt;property name="hibernate.c3p0.idle_test_period"&gt;3000&lt;/property&gt; --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 空闲连接 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 可以将向数据库发送的sql显示出来 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="hibernate.show_sql"&gt;true&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 格式化sql --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="hibernate.format_sql"&gt;true&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- hibernate的方言 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="hibernate.dialect"&gt;org.hibernate.dialect.MySQL5Dialect&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 自动创建表 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="hibernate.hbm2ddl.auto"&gt;update&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 用于设置事务提交方式 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="hibernate.connection.autocommit"&gt;false&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	&lt;!-- 配置hibernate的映射文件所在位置 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="myeclipse.connection.profile"&gt;ddq&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name=<span class="string">"connection.url"</span>&gt;jdbc:mysql:<span class="comment">//localhost:3306/plane?useSSL=true&amp;amp;user=root&amp;amp;password=1234567hy&amp;amp;characterEncoding=utf8&lt;/property&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="connection.username"&gt;root&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="connection.password"&gt;1234567hy&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="connection.driver_class"&gt;com.mysql.jdbc.Driver&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;property name="dialect"&gt;org.hibernate.dialect.MySQLDialect&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;mapping resource=<span class="string">"com/po/passenger.hbm.xml"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;mapping resource=<span class="string">"com/po/orders.hbm.xml"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;mapping resource=<span class="string">"com/po/plane.hbm.xml"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">	&lt;mapping resource=<span class="string">"com/po/flight.hbm.xml"</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/session-factory&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;/hibernate-configuration&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
